          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Businesses controlled by a major financial supporter of President Donald Trump have seen a huge growth in payouts from the United States Postal Service during the Trump administration, a TMI review has found.",
            "type": "text",
